document_data.name: Halanaestra
document_data.mainbody: '''Halanaestra''' was an [[elf]] of mixed [[wild elf]] and [[moon elf]] heritage (and possibly [[aquatic elf]], too).
document_data.History: Around [[1368 DR]], she was the proprietor of the [[Green Sword]] tavern in [[Leuthilspar]], [[Evermeet]]. Prior to this, she was a famous dancer.
